cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.DL 

This paper deals with the analysis of texts written in English and Spanish, and the measurement of entropy and symbolic diversity. It also evaluates the relationship between the quality of writing and readability indices. This work involves natural language processing, machine learning, and information retrieval, which are all relevant to the sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), and deep learning (cs.DL).
